Create module score

DefaultAssay(integrated.lung.filtered) <- "SCT"
Idents(integrated.lung.filtered) <- "main.annotation"

integrated.lung.filtered <- AddModuleScore(
  object = integrated.lung.filtered,
  features = hallmark.p53.mouse, nbin = 10, 
  ctrl = 25,
  name = 'p53_features_SCT')

saveRDS(integrated.lung.filtered, "/udd/rejyu/mouse_singlecell/collaborations/integrated.lung.filtered.Jan11.rds")

p53 scores by cell type and genotype

integrated.lung.filtered <- readRDS("/udd/rejyu/mouse_singlecell/collaborations/integrated.lung.filtered.Jan11.rds")

Idents(integrated.lung.filtered) <- "main.annotation"

ciliated <- subset(x = integrated.lung.filtered, idents = "Ciliated")

ciliated@meta.data <- ciliated@meta.data %>% dplyr::mutate(genotype = ifelse(genotype == "Het", "Hhip+/-", 
                                                                             ifelse(genotype == "Wt", "Hhip+/+", NA)))
Idents(ciliated) <- "genotype"
p <- VlnPlot(ciliated, features = "p53_features_SCT1",  split.by = "genotype", pt.size =0.1)
p + xlab("Genotype") + ylab("p53 pathway score")

wilcox.test(ciliated@meta.data$p53_features_SCT1 ~ ciliated@meta.data$genotype, exact = F)
